comments: Tatum (BOS) releases from contact with Powell (POR) off ball as he attempts to get open.
Nurkic (POR) absorbs the contact from Tatum (BOS) during his driving shot attempt.
Smart (BOS) and Powell (POR) make incidental contact with each other during the rebound.
Brown (BOS) dislodges Lillard (POR) from his legal guarding position as he makes the pass.
Nurkic (POR) moves laterally into Tatum (BOS) and makes body contact that affects his SQBR.
Walker (BOS) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Powell (POR) and absorbs the contact.
Nurkic (POR) reaches in and makes contact to Tatum's (BOS) arm that affects his SQBR.
Williams (BOS) and Nurkic (POR) engage and separate during the rebound.
Lillard (POR) stops short in Smart's (BOS) path during the throw-in and marginal contact occurs.
Smart (BOS) and Lillard (POR) engage during the throw-in and Smart does not dislodge Lillard from his position.
Covington (POR) commits a take foul on Smart (BOS).
